data.description:
2.5% ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE, Beautiful 2018 Kolter Home in Desirable Gated Vizcaya Falls. 3 Bed 2.5 Bath with a Den That Easily Converts to a First Floor 4th Bedroom. This 2 Story Home is Perfect for Generational Living, Space For Everyone.Elegant Glass Door Entryway Leads into an Open Floor Plan with High Ceilings and lots of Light. Both a Formal Dining Room and Eat in Kitchen, Wood Look Tile  throughout the Downstairs, Carpet upstairs, Top Quality Fixtures + Plantation Shutters. A Light & Bright Loft Area and Laundry Room. Enjoy Your Covered Lanai + Beautiful Privacy Palms Out Back, Room for A Pool. Zoned Sprinkler System. Impact Glass Throughout.Residents Pay a Very Low HOA Fee Which Includes a Host of Amenities.At the gate box find Miller A & B then press call. Grand Clubhouse Featuring a Large Pool, Community Room, Billiard & Poker Rooms, Fitness Center, Trails, Basketball Court, Tennis Courts, and a Picnic Area and Playground & Open Fields for everyone to enjoy.
Just a Short Distance to Mets Spring Training Complex, Restaurants, Golf, and the Beaches. Close to I95 & A Short Drive to Shops & Stores in Saint Lucie West.
